ation. Check out summer and fall courses UX + IX Design Workshop series Home Where NEW MEETS NEXT A hub of corporate headquarters, Fortune 1000 companies, and thriving startups, the North Texas region has one of the largest, most vibrant economies in the world. Frisco is at the heart of this economic boom -- located in one of the fastest-growing areas in the country and home to the $5 Billion Mile.  The University of North Texas New College at Frisco, an off-site instructional facility, is providing a workforce business, tech, and people savvy leaders and problem-solvers who can take their companies to the next level.    UNTNewCollegeFrisco on Facebook @UNTFrisco on Twitter Top UNT: Proud Partner of the Dallas Cowboys The partnership between UNT and the Dallas Cowboys creates opportunities for students to engage with the most visible and valuable sports franchise in the world through class projects and internships. Located only 3 minutes from the Dallas Cowboys World Headquarters, the New College at Frisco is at the frontlines of that partnership. Learn more about partnerships with the New College   LEARNING beyond the walls Learn in a collaborative learning environment where ideas, knowledge and creativity flow at the New College. With classrooms powered by the latest technology, you can collaborate, share data, and communicate on platforms used by leading companies--including a dynamic, multi-wall canvas capable of immersing students in live video, applications and document sharing. Whether you're a working professional or a first-time student, you’ll get hands-on experience and career insight that will transform you into a leader. Job-focused LEARNING in the classroom Small Class Sizes and collaborative learning Engagement with industry experts Convenient schedules with face-to-face and online classes We're here for you. Choose to take classes online or at a location that works best for you. Program offerings vary by location. See our locations around the metropl